ygData.messageBody:
heh, I did that too, but without levitate the whole way. to get up I had to
have selo's going, and to get down I put it on walk, no song, crouched, with
sneak on going backwards :) didn't take a lick of damage.

Gleeman, Bard of the 21st Chorus
I saw Rokenn in the flesh, sorta :)
